2443	 * previously defined ( meaning RM_BlockedClientMeasureTimeStart was not called ).
2444	 * 
2445	 * This function is not thread safe, If used in module thread and blocked callback (possibly main thread)
2446	 * simultaneously, it's recommended to protect them with lock owned by caller instead of GIL. */
2447	int RM_BlockedClientMeasureTimeEnd(RedisModuleBlockedClient *bc) {
2448	    // If the counter is 0 then we haven't called RM_BlockedClientMeasureTimeStart
2449	    if (!bc->background_timer)
